channel.title: Rage-Scape 317 - Great Economy - 24 Skills - Many Features
channel.description:
Webclient: www.Rage-Scape.com/play/
All 24 skills work, yes we even have Construction and Dungeoneering! Amazing economy, although there are many shops, most items are hand crafted by skilling and dropped by our 500+ spawned monsters. Great combat and pking, have a challenge in the wilderness with our community or stake at our Duel Arena! We have ancient curses, overloads, extremes, pking armor, pk points, and more to give you a great PvP experience! We have amazing and fun minigames, from the new Dominion Tower, to fighting endless waves of Zombies, capturing the flags at Castle Wars, and more! Tired of having max combat? Want to be above the rest? We have prestiging with ranks and a reward store with awesome un obtainable items! Not only can you cast every spell in all 3 books, we also provide tons of teleports so you can easily get around the server an have fun! We are growing an active community, the staff and I will be hosting many fun events to ensure everyone has a good time, boss trips, double minigame points, double xp, holiday events, games, and more! Dedicated owner willing to code any requests the players are asking for and hiring appropriate staff. Our server has a 24-7 VPS. Hundreds of spawned npc's to train on, including many full dungeons. Every npc has coded drops. We have tons of bosses, and I mean alot! From the great Avatar, to the complete GodWar Dungeon! Are you a gambler? We have a lottery system running 24-7 and perfect dicing! Our cache loads 670+ monsters and items, we have torva, claws, dungeoneering npc's for the skill, etc. Want to be rewarded for being a loyal player? We have a loyalty point system that you can use points to buy the coolest items in the loyalty store! Being loyal is playing often, voting daily, advertising, helping, etc. Tons of more features, and adding updates almost daily! You will never get bored, trust me!
